'''Lunar New Year 2025''' was a limited-time [[VRChat]] promotion tied to the [[wikipedia:Lunar New Year|Lunar New Year]] and the Year of the Snake. The promotion consisted only of a free limited-time [[Special:MyLanguage/Stickers|sticker]] set; no purchasable [[Special:MyLanguage/Shop|Shop]] items were released for it.<ref name="lny2026">[[Lunar New Year 2026]] on ''VRChat Wiki''. Retrieved April 22, 2026.</ref><ref name="stickers-wiki">[https://wiki.vrchat.com/wiki/Stickers "Stickers"] on ''VRChat Wiki''. Retrieved April 22, 2026.</ref>

== Stickers ==
The Lunar New Year sticker set featured the VRChat mascots in Lunar New Year themes. The set's start date is not documented; it ran until January 2025.<ref name="stickers-wiki"/>

* Lanterns
* Envelope Snake
* Fireworks
* Xin Nian Kuai Le
* Lion Dance
* Fai Chun
* Duilian 1
* Duilian 2
* Red Envelope

Full sticker images are documented on [[Special:MyLanguage/Stickers#Lunar_New_Year|Stickers § Lunar New Year]].

